title: Ep 51: Let's Get (Anti) Social!
description: Self Commodification.  It's all around us now. Does the idea of "branding yourself" give you the dry heaves? It should! When did having millions of likes become more important than having a handful of awesome, real life friends? I explore the devolution of human kind thru the abuse of social media and even interview an actual, live Millenial named Erik who gives insight into this phenomenon. Let's get (anti) social!
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
